org.openimaj.math.model.fit

Class SimpleModelFitting<I,D,M extends EstimatableModel<I,D>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.math.model.fit.SimpleModelFitting<I,D,M>
  • Type Parameters:
    I - type of independent data
    D - type of dependent data
    M - concrete type of model learned
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ModelFitting<I,D,M>, RobustModelFitting<I,D,M>

    public class SimpleModelFitting<I,D,M extends EstimatableModel<I,D>>
extends Object
implements RobustModelFitting<I,D,M>
    Example robust fitting, that simply wraps the models estimate method. Inliers and outliers are estimated by verifying the model against the data.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare
